Plan 6-javor (solo) për SmartCloset Lite (web + Supabase)

Java 1 — Scope + bazat

Mbyllim MVP-në: Wardrobe (CRUD + tags + filters), Outfits (krijo/ruaj), Planner (week view + assign outfit), “in laundry”, “recently worn”.
Vendosim stack: Frontend (p.sh. React/Vite + Tailwind), Backend (Supabase DB + Storage).
Skico UI screens (Figma ose thjesht wireframes): Wardrobe, Outfit Builder, Planner, Settings.
Definition of Done: çdo screen funksionon end-to-end me data reale nga Supabase.

Java 2 — Data model + theme UI

Java 2 — Data model + theme UI

Krijo tabelat në Supabase (minimum): items, outfits, outfit_items, plans (plan = outfit + date).
Vendos Storage bucket për foto (ose përkohësisht URL).
Ndërto UI skeleton: layout, navigation, empty states, loading states.

Java 3 — Wardrobe

Implemento Wardrobe CRUD + upload foto + tags.
Search + filters (category/color/tags/season) me performancë të mirë.
“Laundry” status + quick actions në card UI.

Java 4 — Outfit Builder

Krijo outfits nga items (ruajtje + edit + duplicate).
Outfit detail page me “occasion/season notes”.
Validime të thjeshta (p.sh. outfit pa asnjë item s’ruhet).

Java 5 — Planner

Week view + “assign outfit to date”.
“Recently worn” hint (p.sh. në 7 ditët e fundit) + warning nëse një item është “in laundry”.
Export print view (opsionale, nëse del kohë).

Java 6 — Polish + demo-ready

“Fun UX”: drag & drop (opsionale), quick “shuffle outfit”, nice empty states, smooth interactions.
Seed data për demo, testing manual i flows, rregullim bugs.
Deploy (Vercel/Netlify) + dokumentim i thjeshtë (si ta përdorësh).